data.description: Gorgeous Condominium viewing the Gulf Coast Beach from 2 Balconies (one per bedroom). This 2 Bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms fully furnished short term rental, in legal Biloxi commercial zoning allowing it. New LVP flooring in both bedrooms. The living room has new windows (2022). New Vanity sink in the second bathroom. New luxury barn door to bring more privacy in the condo. New TV's (65'' in the living room).   Great location near to the Coliseum, Keesler Airforce Base and Casinos.  Granite counter tops in the kitchen with a back splash, new light fixtures and fans. The HOA cover Internet, water, trash, sewer, and exterior insurance.
